# PenzPilot frontend architecture

See `AGENTS.md` for the full folder map.

## WHERE THINGS LIVE
- **API only:** `src/lib/api-client/`
- **Math:** `src/calculations/`
- **Household defaults:** `src/settings/` + `src/config/moduleDefaults.ts`
- **Static product:** `src/config/`
- **Pure utils:** `src/utils/`
- **Loaders / gates / glue:** `src/helpers/`
- **Cache:** `src/stores/`
- **UI:** `src/components/{domain}/`

## RULES
- **Never** add files to `src/lib/` except under `api-client/`
- Kebab-case files; tuple API `[status, body]`; no `any`
- react-hook-form; modal state on page
- New constants → `config/`
